headline: Teradyne upgraded by Morgan Stanley on Nvidia optimism
summary: Investing.com -- Shares of Teradyne Inc (NASDAQ:TER) were upgraded by Morgan Stanley to equal weight from underweight, saying stronger-than-expected commentary on opportunities with Nvidia (NASDAQ:NVDA) had bolstered investor sentiment.
